{"tid":2226249,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳同佳向潘曉穎父母道歉錄音內容","createTime":"2020-10-02T02:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T02:40:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c3504bebc43509402c49380cf46bf157852c1989","tid":2226249,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T02:19:23.000Z","msg":"香港少女潘曉穎於台北被殺案疑犯陳同佳，今早通過一直協助他的香港聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴，發放錄音，表示已通知台灣代表律師聯絡台灣相關部門，計劃今個月內赴台灣自首。<br />\n<br />\n在錄音中陳同佳再次向潘曉穎父母道歉，表示自己一直沒有改變赴台灣的想法，希望潘曉穎父母放心：<br />\n「潘爸爸、潘媽媽你哋好，我係陳同佳。我再次為曉穎的事情向你們道歉。我返台灣嘅想法一直都冇改變過，我會請我的律師安排返台灣自首的事情，請你哋放心。」<br />\n<br />\n管浩鳴指，「同佳已通知台灣代表律師聯絡相關部門處理他回台自首的安排，期望在十月份內成行。律師將會於台灣假期後，即下星期一進行安排，有進一步消息再通知各位。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%B6%93%E7%AE%A1%E6%B5%A9%E9%B3%B4%E7%99%BC%E6%94%BE%E9%8C%84%E9%9F%B3-%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3-%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A7%E8%B5%B4%E5%8F%B0%E8%87%AA%E9%A6%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E9%25B3%25B4%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2594%25BE%25E9%258C%2584%25E9%259F%25B3-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BD%25B3-%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%2587%25AA%25E9%25A6%2596%2F&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdAkHQxt1T4ELL4DwIHxiqIsg%3D&h=3a82d688\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E9%25B3%25B4%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2594%25BE%25E9%258C%2584%25E9%259F%25B3-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BD%25B3-%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%2587%25AA%25E9%25A6%2596%2F&h=2676e859\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%B6%93%E7%AE%A1%E6%B5%A9%E9%B3%B4%E7%99%BC%E6%94%BE%E9%8C%84%E9%9F%B3-%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3-%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A7%E8%B5%B4%E5%8F%B0%E8%87%AA%E9%A6%96/</a>"},{"pid":"6a6d7b480cba70d62aa6a12c95e5925